slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:52:50.000Z","msg":"理性討論，權衡輕重，塞鐵admin你再考慮下啦。"},{"pid":"f849371a2a8eff9eedbe921eeb74d5cd67110fc8","tid":1459283,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:52:58.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"6deab0c9ff58c09f023b4aa30b13c3209ae2a009","tid":1459283,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:54:09.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"40dd3429296b9de215270ae7f98a6be3ab4ac367","tid":1459283,"uid":52271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"塞鐵不如入機場好過啦"},{"pid":"334b5e1c769a34e02d4a7e2a36ec2f9ba9cc9680","tid":1459283,"uid":270956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"Push  塞鐵手足請聽下人講考慮清楚！<br />\n之前幾次塞鐵行動成效都唔太好，有好多人反感，點解要堅持繼續做？cost係咪大過benefit？<br />\n就算要做都要段時間宣傳，要有原因出師有名，好似之前罷工咁，同埋背後要有民意基礎支持。<br />\n<br />\n818大遊行前，真係唔建議搞呢類爭議性咁大不合作運動，要爭取民意，全力谷多D人參加818大遊行！"},{"pid":"04b3e578d37c8a028eca893ffa2d86844f966750","tid":1459283,"uid":233520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"停一停"},{"pid":"66b13609f1d90d94c8ab89fc27288424dfbd3c1b","tid":1459283,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"28294f2ef3cb0649d7fbdcfac07c1afe1bc88fc2","tid":1459283,"uid":222633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借一借位，我明白唔係每個手足都可以隨便罷工、無限期罷工，所以大家可以做以下簡單基本野<br />\n<br />\n全部人每日黑衫口罩頭盔返工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1452477/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1452477/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ea6ca93994312daa6dcdf6104d4b82bfa014e22a","tid":1459283,"uid":101446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48dde4063b6514d06c06d55c09d2174778d5a212","tid":1459283,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"我地好多人都明 要組織