作運動阻人返工係百分百失民心同擾民<br />\n你塞到一條線意義不大，時間又塞唔長<br />\n只會比位政府同林奠比位入<br />\n所以大家推<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">塞鐵不如一齊去機場imax睇戲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9cdbc4fabbf53d86464f35f2614d6df2276b48","tid":1459283,"uid":40442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"認同塞鐵效用唔大, 機場經濟打擊港共政權有效率啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e36d4367a2f847cb9d446165a0e1acf78c7324","tid":1459283,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:07:57.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"04004138b0ac5517d6a9b40bb82f5fd26a94df2c","tid":1459283,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:09:14.000Z","msg":"塞鐵只有反效果，上次唔係已經試過？"},{"pid":"12ff73fa092dd79a0988971fce674b810839edc0","tid":1459283,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70b529ccb3dcc182e69ab0afc8a77085de59d20","tid":1459283,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"塞黎真係把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左帶來民憤同俾人屌之外零作用<br />\n是但係街搵個位貼Poster都有用過塞鐵佔路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdae71686c351e3d74b3eba0cbe30195695d953a","tid":1459283,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"塞我覺得要配合大型罷工<br />\n醫護竟然最先企出黎<br />\n望其他界別都可以組織到"},{"pid":"35bf25d1b780d0bbec80f77a7bd7b74e449b3ed7","tid":1459283,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"5978217fe40fb0c2d9a13a9889f624526d69327b",